flavor_text_entries.red:
Lives in the
shadows of tall
trees where it eats insects. It
is attracted by
light at night.
flavor_text_entries.blue:
Lives in the
shadows of tall
trees where it eats insects. It
is attracted by
light at night.
flavor_text_entries.yellow:
Its large eyes act
as radars. In a
bright place, you can see that they
are clusters of
many tiny eyes.
flavor_text_entries.gold:
Its eyes also
function as radar
units. It catches and eats small
bugs that hide in
darkness.
flavor_text_entries.silver:
Poison oozes from
all over its body.
It catches and eats small bugs at
night that are at­
tracted by light.
flavor_text_entries.crystal:
The small bugs it
eats appear only
at night, so it sleeps in a hole
in a tree until
night falls.
flavor_text_entries.ruby:
VENONAT is said to have evolved with
a coat of thin, stiff hair that covers
its entire body for protection. It possesses large eyes that never fail
to spot even miniscule prey.

flavor_text_entries.firered:

active in darkness. The eyes can also
shoot powerful beams.
